properties.name: Neal Dunn
properties.biography: Neal Dunn, a Representative from Florida; born in Boston, Suffolk County, Mass., February 16, 1953; B.S., Washington & Lee University, Lexington, Va.; M.D., George Washington University, Washington, D.C.; United States Army, 1989-2010; urologist; banker; elected as a Republican to the One Hundred Fifteenth Congress (January 3, 2017-present).
